{"tid":1668903,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"【文宣】畫畫撚國際戰線同四格漫畫巴合作緊喇！","createTime":"2019-10-22T09:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T03:36:51.000Z","uid":73161,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"266f21ba653547f89eb712013014cd3f7d15a8ae","tid":1668903,"uid":73161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:00:52.000Z","msg":"Hello又係Freetoberhk2019團隊,<br />\n相信畫畫撚們對＃freetoberhk2019 都唔陌生！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">【畫畫撚國際戰線】召集！我要推到有得上10月日程表呀！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605599</a></span><br />\n<br />\n為咗令外國人更易入口，除咗出post整合之外，我哋而家仲同四格漫畫巴合作，將漫畫翻譯成唔同嘅語言！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">[反修例文宣] 我畫咗啲四格漫畫式文宣，仲想揾人一齊畫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656358</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四格漫畫巴嘅內容十分update，俾個例子大家睇吓：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6owQoH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6owQoH.jpg&h=72023811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vZ4qW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vZ4qW4.jpg&h=d8d86383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">【狂賀】因為大家嘅積極參與，我哋已經收到二千四百幾個投稿，在此感謝大家咁俾貨！我哋要繼續努力！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qgeOcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qgeOcc.jpg&h=a9d4239f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家積極參與，齊齊follow～<br />\n歡迎文宣組用我哋d material做外國文宣/周圍貼！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIG：@Freetoberhk2019<br />\nFB:Freetober HK 2019<br />\nTG Channel：<a href=\"http://t.me/freetoberhk2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreetoberhk2019&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=e850e375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/freetoberhk2019</a><br />\nTW：@Freetoberhk2019"},{"pid":"4bad3de4e3b83f7437d607e9b62f59533994a86c","tid":1668903,"uid":73161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LcmRQCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcmRQCA.jpg&h=4f1a7d50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中文版自推"},{"pid":"dfa269eb40685fa5f253e010036e258323438a98","tid":1668903,"uid":73161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCkje4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCkje4p.jpg&h=ec05aa96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英文版自推"},{"pid":"05ff9915a764215f1899d6f99594bb0a09734441","tid":1668903,"uid":73161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJL7oXX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJL7oXX.jpg&h=fe91e168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西班牙文版自推"},{"pid":"553d14ddc39bded96d2d098c9320360770b4e0a2","tid":1668903,"uid":73161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLoEe4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLoEe4Y.jpg&h=0e8875de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日文版自推"},{"pid":"03eade048a12145b6a19ee9dacd7377dc84bd839","tid":1668903,"uid":73161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bToAxSR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbToAxSR.jpg&h=057cdb89&s={SIZE}\" /><br